{"tid":1287981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［快backup］畫家手稿流出","createTime":"2019-07-05T12:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T02:18:05.000Z","uid":70888,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"66ff6e060261d33e7a4b1de144f7ca319e4c527b","tid":1287981,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:15:29.000Z","msg":"畫家達文西<br />\n<br />\n達文西是很有名氣的畫家，在他很小的時候就對各種各樣的事情都很感興趣，他在年輕的時候非常喜歡畫畫，所以留下了一大筆畫作手稿，達文西的這些繪畫手稿大部分都是以素描為底的所以保存的比較久，但是達文西除了是非常出色的畫家之外他還在非常多的方面都有過研究，比較特別的就是達文西手稿還有非常多是有關於醫學方面的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLYUmSK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLYUmSK.png&h=873956d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://read01.com/zh-hk/naPk6N.html#image-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2Fzh-hk%2FnaPk6N.html%23image-1&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BPDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=ff8bab71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/zh-hk/naPk6N.html#image-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快backup, 畫家達文西手稿好有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知你地毅進仔唔識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上面比埋條link你地搵料back up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a7ee845e2e73dc702b2fec0be621bd6775443a","tid":1287981,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"毅進仔要識多d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bb22a40b559e78938873b111a16454551f5ba2","tid":1287981,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係識汪汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19878b09333ed61ba9f1bf981e4ef9fd2eb4c093","tid":1287981,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12